description:
A basic 101 of Computer science

Updated quality of the content based on customer feedback

Introduction,
Number system,
computer hardware,
Operating system,
Programming,
Object oriented programming,
Databases,
Data structures,
Sorting,
Networking and internet,
Software engineering,
Project management,
Introduction to algorithms,
Sorting algorithms,
Heap and quick sort,
Searching algorithms.


Also includes search feature.
